    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes a method of providing privacy for UAS
   Operator/Pilot information specified in the ASTM UAS Remote ID and
   Tracking messages.  This is achieved by encrypting, in place, those
   fields containing Operator sensitive data using a hybrid ECIES.</t>
    </abstract>
